_aChangeLog.text: Redid ramp clips and fixed many of the ramp glitch issues

_sText:
surf_progress is a Tier 2 map including 4 stages and an alternative linear-style route.

The map was designed to act as a tutorial for new players, providing descriptions and examples to learn essential techniques such as strafing, boarding, and flicking.

This map is a port of a collab submission by Xtra (me) and Sam for the CS:GO Skill Surf Mapping Contest.

Enjoy!
